WEBVTT

00:00:00.622 --> 00:00:02.622
(Yuma)
Last time on
Yu-Gi-Oh! Zexal.

00:00:03.888 --> 00:00:05.488
(Astral)
He is going to
use Hart's power

00:00:05.521 --> 00:00:08.921
as a trigger to fire
the Sphere Field Cannon.

00:00:08.954 --> 00:00:13.488
(Dr. Faker)
Once Astral world is destroyed,
Barian's power will be mine!

00:00:13.521 --> 00:00:18.788
And with that this entire
world will kneel before me!

00:00:18.821 --> 00:00:21.054
(Yuma)
We can do
this together!

00:00:21.088 --> 00:00:23.654
This is it!

00:00:31.521 --> 00:00:34.954
(Dr. Faker)
Your end begins now.

00:00:34.988 --> 00:00:36.721
I'm going
to unleash a force

00:00:36.754 --> 00:00:40.021
greater than anything
you've ever faced!

00:00:40.054 --> 00:00:42.154
It is draining the
other Numbers' power.

00:00:42.188 --> 00:00:44.421
I feel myself
growing weaker.

00:00:44.454 --> 00:00:48.888
I Xyz Summon,
Number 53, Heart-Earth!

00:00:50.154 --> 00:00:52.054
Utopia!

00:00:52.088 --> 00:00:54.954
Rising Sun Slash!

00:00:54.988 --> 00:00:57.888
Shark Drake, finish
off that Heart-Earth.

00:00:57.921 --> 00:01:00.321
Deep Sea Destruction!

00:01:02.254 --> 00:01:05.288
Galaxy-Eyes
Photon Dragon, attack!

00:01:05.321 --> 00:01:07.921
Photon Stream
of Destruction!

00:01:10.554 --> 00:01:11.688
No way.

00:01:11.721 --> 00:01:13.454
Is it over?

00:01:16.988 --> 00:01:19.388
<i>(Yuma)
It looks like
Faker survived...</i>

00:01:19.421 --> 00:01:22.254
<i>only now he's
got a new friend.</i>

